main event: A civilian observer reported sighting a pulsating light resembling an aircraft in Germantown, Tennessee on December 12, 1968.
interesting points: The observation lasted between 5 to 8 minutes., The object was seen moving in an ENE to SSW course., The observer considered the object a probable aircraft., The witness reportedly attempted to photograph the object but no photographs are present in the report., There was no physical evidence collected regarding the sighting.
